728841f-b.title: Richmond: Forest Avenue - Duer Lane
728841f-b.text:
(1)
Forest Ave. (background), west from Duer Lane to Haven
Esplanade. The houses are on the north side of the avenue. The
view is across the northeastern edge of Silver Lake Park.
April 16, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
The same, at a later date.
July s, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

728833f-a.title: Richmond: Forest Avenue - Duer Lane
728833f-a.text:
63 Forest Ave., north side, between Duer Lane and Haven
Esplanade, ahowing the Louis A. Dreyfus residence.
May 1927.
P. L. Sperm.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
